Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.03,Kaho,,0,0,0,,You did it, Rurino-chan!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.63,0:08:24.05,Kaho,,0,0,0,,It’s gotta be because of all the energy we sent from offstage!\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:13.06,Kaho,,0,0,0,,Oh? Looks like Megumi-senpai’s getting embarrassed~.\N{\fs40}[Kaho]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,For the love of…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.86,0:00:34.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,why would she change so suddenly…?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.03,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Rurino-san.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:49.38,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi just dropped by and told us to get rid of her stuff.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.96,0:00:53.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,We ended up having to go all the way to the warehouse as a result.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.01,0:01:06.27,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Possibly…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:18.48,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I guess something did happen.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:45.92,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Megumi was the hardest worker I knew.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.25,0:01:57.27,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…And what did she say?\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:46.06,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…You really have quite the memory.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:33.33,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on making your comeback, Megumi.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:49.13,Kozue,,0,0,0,,…I-It’s not as if I was waiting for you or anything…\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.64,0:08:55.60,Kozue,,0,0,0,,Your stuff is all still in the clubroom, so it’ll be your responsibility to take it back to the warehouse.\N{\fs40}[Kozue]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.19,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Every time I look at these shoes, I think to myself,\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.07,0:02:11.92,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’ve run really far, haven’t I?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:17.57,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And if there was a girl out there that could catch up to me…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:25.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Then I’d have no choice but to make an unbeatable unit with her to captivate the whole world, right?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.21,0:03:04.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Huh? R-Ruri-chan…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:05.71,Megumi,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.91,Megumi,,0,0,0,,H-Huh? About what…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.03,0:03:28.33,Megumi,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, you’re gonna bother people…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.54,Megumi,,0,0,0,,ugh, fine, just get inside!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:49.60,Megumi,,0,0,0,,These are just…!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.04,0:03:52.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I-I only use them to go running sometimes!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:56.20,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Like when I go for a breather and stuff!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:04:00.42,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And I figured I’d keep buying the shoes I’m used to wearing…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:16.40,Megumi,,0,0,0,,N-No…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:21.50,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I shouldn’t have lied to you in the first place.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:34.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.98,0:04:41.50,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:52.09,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.57,Megumi,,0,0,0,, I… I…  \N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.52,0:06:06.32,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.02,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.12,0:06:10.97,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I…!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:18.40,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No matter how many times I stumble and fall, the only thing I can’t do is give up!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:21.88,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Because…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.95,0:06:25.46,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Because you’re waiting for me!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:49.73,Megumi,,0,0,0,,That’s not true.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.69,0:06:52.50,Megumi,,0,0,0,,You were cool, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:56.06,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Very, very cool.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:05.79,Megumi,,0,0,0,,No, no.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:08.40,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The one who came for me was you, Ruri-chan.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:16.50,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hehehe.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.10,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Ruri-chan!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.62,Megumi,,0,0,0,,The two of us will captivate the whole world!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.35,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Okay, everyone!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:34.68,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Let’s get fired up today!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.19,0:07:37.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m gonna do my usual thing, ‘kay~? ☆\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:41.45,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Everyone! HelloMegu!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:54.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And our name is…!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
