Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:34.78,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:41.47,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And sorry for worrying you two so much, Kozue, Tsuzuri.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:42.99,Megumi,,0,0,0,,And…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:44.99,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m back.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:02.76,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Y-Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.96,0:09:08.63,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Ahaha, all this fanfare is a little embarrassing…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.40,Megumi,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:23.31,Megumi,,0,0,0,,I’m a year above you two, so you should still respect me, you know! Hmph!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.09,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hm, hm…!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.65,0:09:41.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Yeah…\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:43.86,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruri-chan?\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:47.75,Megumi,,0,0,0,,…Sorry for being so stubborn.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:55.42,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Honestly… I’m really, really happy you came here.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:59.22,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Thank you, from the bottom of my heart.\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.54,Megumi,,0,0,0,,So!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:12.73,Megumi,,0,0,0,,Next time, let’s stand on stage, together, from the very beginning!\N{\fs40}[Megumi]
