Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.45,NPC,,0,0,0,,HelloMegu!\N{\fs40}[Crowd]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.14,0:00:03.92,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.49,0:00:10.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I didn’t know anything about her this whole time..\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.11,0:00:16.08,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Yet I still had the nerve to act like she was my best friend…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:21.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Is it really too late now…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.98,0:00:26.37,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Was this… all for nothing…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.52,0:00:40.32,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Kozue-senpai, Tsuzuri-senpai…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.28,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Does that mean…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:01:03.26,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan won’t be coming back to the School Idol Club…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.03,0:01:08.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,It’s all my fault…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.18,0:01:12.82,Rurino,,0,0,0,,All because I pushed her too hard…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.35,0:01:20.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Huh…?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Those shoes…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:25.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I never noticed…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:28.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Those are the shoes I gave Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.67,0:01:32.87,Rurino,,0,0,0,,They’re different sizes, but they’re all the same kind…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:36.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,They’re so worn out…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.05,0:01:39.16,Rurino,,0,0,0,,She must’ve practiced so much in these…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.67,0:01:40.92,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I never knew…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.45,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I-I’ve gotta go!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan! Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:08.21,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Listen! I finally figured it out!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.21,0:03:10.60,Rurino,,0,0,0,,About you! And about me!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:19.42,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I didn’t come to like you because you were so cool, or because you could do anything.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:22.64,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I like you because you’re you, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.64,0:03:25.03,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve always thought that way!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:46.52,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Oh… those shoes…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,you have them here, too…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.45,0:04:05.65,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Megu-chan.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.62,0:04:13.56,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry for not noticing how hard you’ve been working this whole time.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:26.41,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You always shone the way forward for me.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.15,0:04:30.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And yet, I only made things harder for you…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.41,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:37.12,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.06,0:04:40.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But I’ll be okay now!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:46.54,Rurino,,0,0,0,,This time, I’ll be the one guiding you forward!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.71,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m way stronger than I was back then!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:57.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I spent two years in California, a place filled with people I didn’t know, all by myself!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:02.01,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And just like we promised, I got big and came back!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:08.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Maybe you don’t think I’m ready yet, but I mean it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:11.24,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll be okay!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:16.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ve gotten waaay stronger, and I’m gonna prove it to you!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:21.02,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll show you a new Ruri!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:22.86,Rurino,,0,0,0,,So let’s do it!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:26.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Let’s be school idols, together!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:28.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,What’s done is done!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,The past is in the past!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.63,0:05:36.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,From now on, I’ll pull you forward, and you’ll pull me forward too!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:38.14,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We’ll be a new MeguRuri!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.57,0:05:41.46,Rurino,,0,0,0,,We can start fresh, right here!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.99,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’ll be waiting, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:31.70,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.73,Rurino,,0,0,0,,A-Ahaha…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.73,0:06:41.69,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Performing by myself is pretty tough…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:48.09,Rurino,,0,0,0,,But it’s kinda sad that I’m like this after trying to act so cool earlier, y’know…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:59.13,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Ahaha, thanks…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.63,0:07:04.45,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan, thanks for coming!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:15.06,Rurino,,0,0,0,,S-stop it, you’re gonna make me cry up on stage!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.40,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Okay then, Megu-chan!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Let’s do this together!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.61,0:07:46.77,Rurino,,0,0,0,,And, and!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:52.55,Rurino,,0,0,0,,The two of us are a subunit from the Hasunosora School Idol Club!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.77,0:07:56.22,Rurino,,0,0,0,,One, two…!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.25,0:08:10.81,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Gah…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.81,0:08:13.25,Rurino,,0,0,0,,I’m exhausted…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.03,0:08:17.83,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Agh.\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:26.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,T-Time-out!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,My battery’s totally drained right now!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.47,Rurino,,0,0,0,,If you cling to me like that, I’ll die! I’m dying!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:26.00,Rurino,,0,0,0,,Megu-chan! {\i1}Good job!{\i0}\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:30.76,Rurino,,0,0,0,,You really, really worked hard today!\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.04,Rurino,,0,0,0,,M-Megu-chan…\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.40,Rurino,,0,0,0,,A-Ah-huh!?\N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:15.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,…Yeah! \N{\fs40}[Rurino]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:17.63,Rurino,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.07,0:08:20.26,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,Your performance was a great success!\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:16.40,Sayaka,,0,0,0,,This side of her is surprisingly cute, huh?\N{\fs40}[Sayaka]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.36,0:00:36.01,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Right?\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:49.49,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,You know, I asked her once.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:54.46,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,I wondered why she kept all these shoes.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.15,0:01:59.08,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,She said…  \N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:38.94,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where–\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:40.74,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,And she’s gone.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:47.58,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,It was…\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.15,0:02:51.56,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,a lot of fun.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:53.42,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Of course I remember.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.40,Tsuzuri,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Megu.\N{\fs40}[Tsuzuri]
